title: Smart 'Esquites' Bacon and Corn Chowder with Sour Cream and Feta
description: Let the flavours of the beloved Mexican street snack "elotes" in this reimagined stew version warm your hearts and your bellies. Our chowder is topped with crispy bacon bits and tangy sour cream – it's the perfect balance of textures and flavours.

